==English==

===Pronunciation===
*mĭngk, /mɪŋk/, /<tt>mINk</tt>/

===Noun===
'''mink''' (''see individual definitions for plurals'')

#(''plural'' '''mink''') Any of various [[semi-aquatic]], [[carnivorous]] [[mammal]], similar to a [[weasel]], with dark [[fur]] and native to [[Europe]] and [[America]].
#(''plural'' '''[[minks]]''') A [[mink coat]].

